38:41.959 --> 38:43.625
WHAT DO YOU WANT?

38:52.208 --> 38:56.000
♪ BABE ♪

38:56.083 --> 38:59.500
♪ THERE'S SOMETHING TRAGIC
ABOUT YOU ♪

38:59.583 --> 39:01.041
OKAY?

39:01.125 --> 39:03.709
♪ SOMETHING SO MAGIC ABOUT YOU ♪

39:03.792 --> 39:06.792
NOT OKAY.
♪ DON'T YOU AGREE? ♪

39:09.125 --> 39:12.875
♪ BABE ♪

39:12.959 --> 39:16.709
♪ THERE'S SOMETHING LONESOME
ABOUT YOU ♪

39:16.792 --> 39:20.125
♪ SOMETHING
SO WHOLESOME ABOUT YOU ♪

39:20.208 --> 39:24.625
♪ GET CLOSER TO ME ♪

39:27.709 --> 39:29.458
WHOA,
DID YOU JUST GET BACK?

39:29.542 --> 39:30.959
YEAH, IT TOOK FOREVER.
WELL, SLOW DOWN.

39:31.041 --> 39:33.458
I HAVEN'T BROKEN IN
THIS NEW SET OF STICKS.

39:33.542 --> 39:34.625
[ SIGHS ] WHAT'S UP?

39:34.709 --> 39:36.333
GOOD NEWS.

39:36.417 --> 39:38.959
DR. McANDREW'S ALREADY GOT
THE CAR BACK FROM THE TOW PLACE.

39:39.041 --> 39:41.792
BAD NEWS, THE IGUANA ATE
THE ORIGAMI PAPER.

39:41.875 --> 39:43.625
WORSE NEWS,
IT'S ESCAPED.

39:43.709 --> 39:46.083
SO WE STILL HAVE NOTHING
FOR CHARLIE.
NO, NOT TODAY.

39:46.166 --> 39:48.709
BUT DASH AND I STILL FIGURED
WE COULD DO THE PIZZA THING.

39:48.792 --> 39:50.417
YOU KNOW,
I KNOW IT'S NOT PERFECT,

39:50.500 --> 39:51.750
BUT IT'S BETTER
THAN NOTHING, RIGHT?

39:51.834 --> 39:53.166
MM-HMM.

39:53.250 --> 39:54.417
YOU KNOW YOU DON'T
HAVE TO EAT THE PIZZA.

39:54.500 --> 39:56.959
I KNOW THAT. THANKS.
OKAY.

39:58.250 --> 40:01.000
SORRY.
UM, I'M JUST WIPED.

40:01.083 --> 40:02.625
WHY DON'T YOU GUYS
START WITHOUT ME?

40:02.709 --> 40:04.667
I'M GONNA -- I'M GONNA GO
LIE DOWN FOR A BIT.

40:04.750 --> 40:06.500
OKAY.

40:06.583 --> 40:08.166
[ DAUGHTER'S "MEDICINE" PLAYS ]

40:08.250 --> 40:11.291
[ SIGHS ]

40:23.583 --> 40:26.834
HELLO.

40:26.917 --> 40:28.333
[ TRIANGLE RINGS ]

40:28.417 --> 40:29.959
MY NEW DINNER BELL.
DR. NADAY GAVE IT TO ME.

40:30.041 --> 40:31.125
I'M GETTING
REALLY GOOD AT IT.

40:31.208 --> 40:32.792
I'M NOT HUNGRY.

40:32.875 --> 40:35.125
OH, WELL,
I THINK YOU MIGHT RECONSIDER

40:35.208 --> 40:37.000
WHEN YOU SEE
WHAT I BROUGHT.

40:37.083 --> 40:38.458
♪ PICK IT UP, PICK IT ALL UP ♪
THEY'RE LITTLE HEARTS.

40:38.542 --> 40:39.709
I USED A COOKIE CUTTER.

40:39.792 --> 40:41.834
PLEASE JUST
LEAVE ME ALONE.

40:41.917 --> 40:43.166
♪ AND START AGAIN ♪

40:43.250 --> 40:44.959
OF COURSE.

40:45.041 --> 40:47.834
UM, BUT I AM GONNA NEED YOU
TO HAVE SOME DINNER, EMMA.

40:47.917 --> 40:49.834
YOUR WEIGH-IN
IS AT 9:00.

40:49.917 --> 40:51.542
♪ YOU'VE GOT A SECOND CHANCE ♪

40:51.625 --> 40:54.125
♪ YOU COULD GO HOME ♪

40:54.208 --> 40:56.166
♪ ESCAPE IT ALL ♪

40:56.250 --> 40:59.667
♪ IT'S JUST IRRELEVANT ♪

41:03.500 --> 41:06.375
♪ IT'S JUST MEDICINE ♪

41:09.291 --> 41:13.667
♪ IT'S JUST MEDICINE ♪

41:23.333 --> 41:26.083
[ SIGHS ] THIS IS STARTING
TO FEEL STRANGE.

41:26.166 --> 41:27.583
MAYBE
WE SHOULD PARTAKE.

41:27.667 --> 41:29.917
IT DOES
SMELL REALLY GOOD.

41:30.000 --> 41:31.250
YOU COOL WITH THAT,
CHARLIE?

41:32.792 --> 41:34.875
OKAY.

41:34.959 --> 41:37.917
HEY, LOOK, I'M SORRY.

41:38.000 --> 41:40.166
THIS ISN'T EXACTLY
WHAT WE HAD PLANNED.

41:40.250 --> 41:43.041
<i>ARE YOU KIDDING?</i>
<i>THIS IS AWESOME.</i>

41:43.125 --> 41:44.542
<i>I MEAN,</i>
<i>BOOBS WOULD HAVE BEEN NICE.</i>

41:44.625 --> 41:46.375
<i>BUT HANGING WITH MY FRIENDS?</i>

41:46.458 --> 41:48.583
<i>NOT A BAD WAY TO SPEND</i>
<i>YOUR FIRST DAY OUT OF A COMA.</i>

41:48.667 --> 41:50.417
<i>AND ANOTHER EXAMPLE</i>
<i>OF HOW SOMETIMES</i>

41:50.500 --> 41:51.959
<i>THE BEST THINGS HAPPEN</i>

41:52.041 --> 41:53.750
<i>WHEN YOU DON'T TRY</i>
<i>TO CONTROL THEM.</i>

41:53.834 --> 41:57.041
[ REUBEN AND THE DARK'S
"CAN'T SEE THE LIGHT" PLAYS ]

41:58.834 --> 42:02.917
<i>FOR SOME PEOPLE,</i>
<i>IT'S EASY TO LOSE CONTROL.</i>

42:03.000 --> 42:04.250
IF YOU HUM IT,
I'LL PLAY IT.

42:04.333 --> 42:05.750
[ LAUGHTER ]

42:05.834 --> 42:08.583
<i>FOR OTHERS, NOT SO MUCH.</i>

42:08.667 --> 42:12.083
♪ IT'S IN MY HEART, IN MY BED ♪

42:12.166 --> 42:15.417
♪ RIDE THE BULLET
TO IN MY HEAD ♪

42:15.500 --> 42:18.917
♪ IT'S IN MY SOUL,
SKIN AND BONE ♪

42:19.000 --> 42:21.250
♪ I'M ON THE LOAD ♪

42:21.333 --> 42:23.000
<i>BUT THE TRUTH IS,</i>

42:23.083 --> 42:25.458
<i>THE MORE WE FEEL</i>
<i>THE NEED TO CONTROL THINGS,</i>

42:25.542 --> 42:28.458
<i>THE MORE THOSE THINGS BEGIN</i>
<i>TO CONTROL US.</i>

42:28.542 --> 42:31.959
♪ LOVE IS NOT THE FINAL WORD ♪

42:32.041 --> 42:37.125
♪ LOVE IS NOT
A PRETTY WORD ♪

